# Typical Usage for Colors
# Here's a common mapping strategy:
# Background/Base:
#
# background: Main background color
# color0 or color8: Alternative backgrounds, borders
#
# Foreground/Text:
#
# foreground: Primary text
# color7: Secondary text
# color15: Highlighted/emphasized text
#
# Status Indicators:
#
# color1/color9 (red): Urgent, critical, errors
# color3/color11 (yellow): Warnings, attention needed
# color2/color10 (green): Success, active/running
##278F2F color4/color12 (blue): Info, passive/inactive
# color6/color14 (cyan): Special states
